_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports Scene\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with CGTN Sports Scene's Greg Laffradi, the inspirational veteran shared her excitement as well as how she managed to stay competitive at this age.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.395760475821393e-22, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"the inspirational veteran\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"her excitement\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"this age\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Very exciting.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my first Olympics, so I feel very happy and excited,\\\" Zeng said.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first Olympics\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"Zeng\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the Olympic stage, I just wanted to show my real abilities.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"my real abilities\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes at the Olympics are all very excellent, so I accomplished my task by just showing what I have got.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"my task\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no difference among ages in competitions.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no difference\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"ages\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will face whoever you are against, no matter the age.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel I am much older than them.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel we are the same as competitors.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are equal on either side of the table.\\\"\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"either side\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zeng became a professional player when she was 16.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zeng\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional player\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the competitions in the Chinese national team has always been nothing but fierce because of the country's deep pool of talents for table tennis.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999376541938904, \"rank\": 3.953427186580152e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's deep pool\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"talents\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, Zeng wasn't able to play at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"Zeng\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having retired as a player when she was 20, Zeng was then invited to Chile as a table tennis coach.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7295212790028219, \"rank\": 0.3601164287211183, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"Zeng\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"a table tennis coach\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having picked up her paddle again during the COVID-19 pandemic, she was selected into the Chilean national team at 57.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9997789653371053, \"rank\": 0.0001659885384391019, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"htt