tches\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Depending on my physical level, if I can get through the trials and be selected, I will definitely continue playing table tennis.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my physical level\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am not selected, I will still play amateur matches.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amateur matches\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reason why I take part in competitions is that I am happy to play them and put pressure on myself, so I will continue playing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reason\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"010-85061466 SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2267}, {\